These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea, daffodil, marigold, aconite, poppy
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: romance, spy, animation, zombie, sports, epic
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person watching sports movies is between the person who growspoppy and the person watching romance movies##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching spy movies##2
6. the person watching romance movies is the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
8. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
9. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Flower           | amaryllis | azalea | poppy | aconite | marigold    | daffodil  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | spy   | zombie       | sports        | romance | animation |

