.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, boat, scooter, trike, taxi
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: mystery, disaster, documentary, time-travel, horror, family
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the ship##2
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Transport   | quad-bike | taxi | trike | scooter | boat | ship  |
| Movie-Genre           | family | horror  | mystery | disaster    | time-travel  | documentary |

