.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
City: edinburgh, liverpool, miami, nizza, marseilles, venice
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, baccarat, aristoff, oliveros, pall-mall, dunhill
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to nizza and the montecristo-smoker##2
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
8. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| City         | liverpool | edinburgh | venice      | marseilles | nizza | miami      |
| Cigar   | baccarat    | dunhill  | montecristo | oliveros   | pall-mall       | aristoff |

