.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: purple, light-blue, aquamarine, apricot, orange, brown
House: victorian, palace, colonial, art-deco, ranch-style, modern
1. the colonial house is the person who likes apricot##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the victorian house##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the art-deco house is the person who likes light-blue##1
5. the person who likes purple is the victorian house##1
6. the palace house is between the victorian house and the person who likes brown##2
7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
8. the colonial house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Color        | light-blue    | brown | aquamarine | purple | orange | apricot   |
| House   | art-deco | ranch-style        | palace  | victorian     | modern  | colonial |

