The people have 6 different jobs:  dancer, paramedic, doctor, firefighter, engineer, nurse
1. the dancer is on the left of the engineer##1
2. the nurse is the person who growszinnia##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the nurse is on the far right##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the engineer##1
6. the person who growslily is on the right of the paramedic##1
7. the doctor is the person who growslily##1
8. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growsorchid and the nurse##2
9. the person who growsiris is the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Flower    | iris | lily | amaryllis  | orchid      | dahlia | zinnia  |
| Job   | paramedic  | doctor    | firefighter | dancer | engineer | nurse |

