.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: amber, white, yellow, red, emerald, blue
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, january, october, february, august, march
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in may##2
4. the person who likes red is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes white and the person who likes emerald##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
8. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
9. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Color           | red | blue | emerald | yellow | white | amber |
| Birthday   | october   | february   | january         | may    | march     | august     |

