.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
House: tower, wooden, townhouse, cape-cod, gothic-revival, cottage
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, sprite, juice, fanta, coffee
 1. the cottage house is the person drinking juice##1
 2. the person drinking cola is between the tower house and the person drinking coffee##2
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking juice is the cottage house##1
 5. the tower house is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the cottage house##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the wooden house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the wooden house##1
10. the cape-cod house is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| House   | tower   | gothic-revival  | wooden | cape-cod | cottage | townhouse     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola | coffee    | fanta | juice | sprite |

