.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, woodworking, traveling, puzzles, gardening
House: colonial, art-deco, futuristic, craftsman, townhouse, wooden
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the townhouse house##1
 3. the wooden house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 4. the wooden house is on the far right##1
 5. the townhouse house is between the art-deco house and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
 6. the craftsman house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 7. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is the colonial house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the colonial house and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Hobby         | gardening   | puzzles | woodworking       | traveling | drawing    | hiking |
| House   | art-deco | townhouse  | futuristic | colonial      | craftsman | wooden        |

