.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
House: craftsman, tower, gothic-revival, art-deco, palace, colonial
There 6 different types of food: apple, grapefruit, onion, pomegranate, carrot, potato
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 2. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the tower house is the person eating pomegranate##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is between the art-deco house and the person eating potato##2
 5. the person eating onion is between the person eating potato and the palace house##2
 6. the person eating onion is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 7. the tower house is on the far left##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 9. the person eating potato is the craftsman house##1
10. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| House           | tower      | art-deco | gothic-revival | craftsman   | colonial  | palace |
| Food   | pomegranate | apple  | grapefruit             | potato | onion | carrot       |

