3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the brazilian and the thai##2
4. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the malaysian##1
8. the brazilian is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Nationality          | argentine | polish | malaysian | brazilian    | german | thai |
| Sport   | climbing     | rowing | lacrosse   | cycling | snowboarding | water-polo |

