.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, boat, helicopter, train, tram
There are 6 different favourite colors: coral, amber, brown, green, orange, blood-red
 1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person who likes blood-red is between the person who likes orange and the person driving the skateboard##2
 3. the person who likes orange is between the person driving the tram and the person who likes coral##2
 4. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the tram is between the person who likes brown and the person driving the boat##2
 6. the person driving the helicopter is the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 9. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Transport   | helicopter     | scooter | train   | boat     | tram       | skateboard       |
| Color    | amber | green   | coral | orange | blood-red | brown |

