.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, trike, subway, airplane, snowmobile, skateboard
6 different games are played: canasta, billiard, go, poker, monopoly, chess
 1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person playing poker is the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 7. the person playing billiard is the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person playing go is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the scooter##2
10. the person driving the snowmobile is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Transport         | airplane | scooter | trike | skateboard | snowmobile | subway |
| Game   | canasta | monopoly | go      | poker     | chess       | billiard |

 